text: Santi Wibowo (born 15 November 1974) is a Swiss badminton player. She competed in women's singles and mixed doubles at the 1996 Summer Olympics in Atlanta. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1974 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss female badminton players Category:Olympic badminton players of Switzerland Category:Badminton players at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Swiss people of Indonesian descent
